##A game or two on the New Year's Day

Micro-signal Yeguangbeifukan

Function introduction the supplement of Xinmin Evening News, founded on May 1,1946, is the oldest comprehensive supplement of Chinese newspapers.

I would like to see Wuhan's sky with a big Sun, the sun is the embodiment of beauty, through the window lattice, shining on his body.

On the first day of the New Year, I would stay at home and play chess.

Thought ahead, the New Year to pay some debt, check some manuscripts. The winter rain outside the window is endless, a vast expanse of whiteness. Yesterday, Wuhan closed the city, this time to calm down to read the manuscript, a bit difficult.

There is a kind of inertia about the scene if there has been real news for more than twenty years in the golden years of one's life. When something big happens, your mind will want to witness it. Now I have hoary-headed, rare after, is a birth date. Can Not help sighing, this body has been the soul-stirring news scene eliminated.

I have been bound to go all my life. Today, only Weiqi players, like a reed of Daruma, can ferry the players to the West against the current of the Yangtze River to Yellow Crane Tower.

Take off the mask, put on the vest, Open Game City Network, asked: "Wuhan? "

One second, two names came up. One of them is called slow snail, and I'm guessing it's a child. At this moment, I would like to play chess with the children in virus flying foam. He might not have guessed who I was, but he might have seen the word "old" on my waistcoat and imagined me to be one of those once-in-a-lifetime antiques. In, he might be willing to talk to antiques?

I know. I'm in a virtual reality. Drop the first piece, we are face-to-face, in the message board exchange greetings.

"The city is closed, " he said

And I said, "where are you? "

"Hanzhong Street, " he replied

I don't know why I'm being such a pussy. "How are things at home? "

"Everything's fine. "

"It's going to get better. "

"I know. "

The answer to "snail's pace" is only three words.

His chess is very imaginative, belongs to open and close, give up the kind of big transformation, is definitely not the next point under the goal of "snail. ".

So test: "think you are in the prime of life. "

"Sophomore Year. "

This time it's just two words. He was, indeed, a child, not more than sixteen.

He suddenly found himself dead. He said: "Give you a piece. YOU ARE WELCOME! " Is really a proud child. I double-checked to make sure it was a miscalculation, not an intentional abandonment. "He said:"No hurry, but also under

He replied, "mm-hmm. "

The game is over. I stood up and looked back at the bookcase. I have written some articles for go, and I also have many chess books, some of which may be of interest to him.

Back to the computer, the first hit is: "Children, I wish you strong and brave. " is also an Antique Sissy.

Unexpectedly, slow "snail" has been fast fast to go. I looked around the hall, but there was no sign of him. He's offline. The virtual scene has been lifted, he returned to Wuhan, I am still in Shanghai.

Both Games, played in a hurry, add up to less than an hour.

Lost all morning. I miss that kid. In the afternoon, I opened the city net again, in order to see the chess we had played.

On the board, there's a new coronavirus. It was a special meeting. About outside and inside Wuhan City, epidemic area and non-epidemic area, old people and children, virus spread and exterminate. We Sigh and sigh are not chess, but the virus.

One win, one loss, countless mistakes in and out. At this point, go has reverted to the nature of "Talk" . With the form language of Weiqi and the natural language of Chinese, we construct a spiritual space. I looked back at the game and couldn't help but read each other's moods. I want to comfort him, with their own weather-beaten age, as well as in a variety of scenes to obtain life thinking. And I know that, at this very moment, people outside the city... will not be able to say what they mean. What about him? Perhaps he was too eager to tell me, who knew nothing about Wuhan, and US outside the city, that he had a youthful vigor and that the nine-headed bird had its own natural stubbornness.

Slow snail"doesn't sound like a weird vest to me. I would like to read from this an age and his style of chess with a different calm and self-confidence. Now that he's in town, he knows what he has to do.

Checked the weather, Wuhan's weather is overcast, rain and snow. Looking at the map again. Hanzhong street is in Hankou, not too far from the south China Seafood Market. Hanzhong street is a busy place, there are many local snacks, not far from the famous Hanzheng Street shopping mall. There are well-equipped hospitals and good schools around. I don't know what school snail goes to.

Use your imagination to create a space again. I would like to see Wuhan's sky has a big sun, ultraviolet light killed all the virus in the spray. He played chess with his classmates in the classroom with great enthusiasm. The Sun is the embodiment of beauty, through the window lattice, shining on his body. He shouted again "give you" , that is the real abandoned son first, cut off the tail and new life. He went home victorious, carrying a go in his schoolbag and a chessboard in his hand. As he walked down the streets of Hanzhong, the setting sun lengthened his figure and animated his smiling face. Sixteen years old.

I must be infected by his smiling face, so my old face also have a smile. Where am I? Could it be that at a small shop on Hanzhong road, hot and dry noodles with sesame paste and Tamarind are stirred with chopsticks?

Good kids play chess, I guess.
